# Docs: track architecture / strategy / plan docs; ignore working drafts.
# Pattern: ignore everything under /docs/, then re-include named docs that
# follow our architecture-doc convention (UPPER_SNAKE_CASE .md or numbered
# strategy docs). `docs-site/docs/` is the mkdocs source tree and stays
# tracked separately.
/docs/*.docx
/docs/*
!/docs/ARCHE_*.md
!/docs/*PLAN*.md
!/docs/HOW_*.md
!/docs/LLM_*.md
!/docs/ARCHITECTURE_*.md
!/docs/archive/
!/docs/archive/**

/workbook